# 🐢 Turtle Racing Game

A fun interactive racing game built using Python's **Turtle Graphics** module.

The player predicts which colored turtle will win the race before it starts. Each turtle moves forward by a random distance every turn, making every race unique. The game announces whether the player's prediction was correct once a turtle reaches the finish line.

---

## 📌 Features

- Interactive user prediction
- Seven uniquely colored racing turtles
- Randomized race movement
- Automatic winner detection
- Simple graphical interface using Turtle Graphics

